    "description": "<strong>Features: </strong><br><strong>Astral Space Journey:</strong> <br>Take on epic bosses and creatures from the unknown as you embark on a mind bending trek into deep space.<br><br><strong>Original Heavy Metal Soundtrack:</strong> <br>Blast enemies by shredding and wailing your astral guitar against a rolling backing track. Butt-loads of unique riffs and jams to destroy your enemies with during your voyage. Features a full original soundtrack from Dante Morris. <br><br><strong>Hand Drawn Retro Style:</strong> <br>Every character and sprite is hand drawn and animated giving everything a fluid, psychedelic look.<br><br><strong>Randomized Enemy &amp; Item Spawns</strong>: <br>Stages will throw you something different each time.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902810/extras/89c5d465cf30c1c7c2a836645982079e.poster.avif?t=1709617609\" width=800 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902810/extras/89c5d465cf30c1c7c2a836645982079e.webm?t=1709617609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902810/extras/89c5d465cf30c1c7c2a836645982079e.mp4?t=1709617609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Arcade Mode: Voyage across our solar system and beyond as you soar beyond our celestial neighbors into the deep void. <br><br>Hard Mode: Mastered the normal difficulty? Crank up the challenge with Hard mode.<br><br>Endless Mode: Complete Hard difficulty and unlock this mode to go even further into the unknown.<br><br>Stage Select Mode: Unlock various floating pieces of detritus by racing for gold medals!<br><br>Bonus bike stages! Astral aquarium! Easter Eggs! Achievements! Etc!!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902810/extras/5e516545733afe4a5cb9b06da513687f.poster.avif?t=1709617609\" width=800 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902810/extras/5e516545733afe4a5cb9b06da513687f.webm?t=1709617609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902810/extras/5e516545733afe4a5cb9b06da513687f.mp4?t=1709617609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A casual indie game from a solo developer In the spirit of game series like Geometry Wars, Metal Slug, Darius and R-Type.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902810/extras/d2ae8450ffbb88fc722eae71f81188c4.poster.avif?t=1709617609\" width=800 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902810/extras/d2ae8450ffbb88fc722eae71f81188c4.webm?t=1709617609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902810/extras/d2ae8450ffbb88fc722eae71f81188c4.mp4?t=1709617609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
